# Trivy ignore file
#
# Format: one CVE / misconfig ID per line. Anything after `#` is a
# comment. Document *why* a finding is suppressed so reviewers can
# revisit when the upstream advisory changes.

# DS-0002: Dockerfile/Dockerfile.dev run as root.
# Frontend currently uses `nginx:alpine` listening on :80, which
# requires root for the privileged port. Switching to the
# `nginx-unprivileged` image (port 8080, non-root user) is the
# proper fix but requires coordinated changes in the deployment
# repo (Ansible/Terraform/reverse-proxy). Tracked separately —
# see issue #44.
AVD-DS-0002
